text: Aphrodite is the eleventh studio album by Australian singer Kylie Minogue. It was released worldwide in July 2010 by Parlophone Records. The album contains four singles, "All the Lovers", "Get Outta My Way", "Better Than Today" and "Put Your Hands Up (If You Feel Love)". The four singles have all reached number one on the Billboard Hot Dance Club Songs chart. ==Track listing== == References == == Other websites == *Official website of Kylie Minogue Category:2010 albums Category:Kylie Minogue albums Category:Dance-pop albums
